{"id": "1451827729451192360", "channel_id": "1451069244455391465", "type": 19, "author_id": "452609886170251265", "author_name": "tksn.", "author_bot": false, "content": "\"In our regular gacha, we’ve reduced some extreme outcomes in order to provide more stable drops in everyday pulls\"\nso you are confirming that the gacha rules are a lie? why is this reduction not explained in the rules?\nwhat proof do you have that the probabilities and the rates match? do you think we will take your word for it when you have already confirmed you are changing the gacha rates behind the scenes without explaining it to the users?\nKorean studio NEXON was sued for lying about their gacha rules and hiding how it works. do you think you are immune to legal action because you are a smaller company?", "timestamp": "2025-12-20T06:45:04.356000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["633215996508766229"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1451826806616363192", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1451069244455391465", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Question regarding the SSR Item Drop Rate listed in the Awakening Details", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480", "1181168103141416960", "1361169005435420785", "1361168893200044183"]}
{"id": "1451829817614930004", "channel_id": "1451069244455391465", "type": 19, "author_id": "452609886170251265", "author_name": "tksn.", "author_bot": false, "content": "2017 年文化部不是已经出台法规，要求所有虚拟道具的抽取概率必须公示吗？你们公布了概率，却又说对系统做过调整。你觉得我们会相信你们调整系统的同时，却没有改动概率吗？\n\n如果现在公布的概率和实际概率依然一致，那你们当初为什么要改系统？单抽和五连抽的机制明显不一样，却还要我们相信你们“善意”地保证概率完全相同？上面列出的数据已经证明你们公示的概率是有问题的，那到底是你们在撒谎，还是你们团队连最基本的数学都算不明白？如果是撒谎，那我们凭什么现在还要相信你们会诚实？如果是算不明白，那我们又凭什么相信你们修改后的系统真的符合你们所宣称的概率？", "timestamp": "2025-12-20T06:53:22.213000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["633215996508766229"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1451826806616363192", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1451069244455391465", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Question regarding the SSR Item Drop Rate listed in the Awakening Details", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480", "1181168103141416960", "1361169005435420785", "1361168893200044183"]}
