{"id": "1451736016032628970", "channel_id": "1451736016032628970", "type": 0, "author_id": "335454645251997717", "author_name": "iwthahe", "author_bot": false, "content": "In the picture below are 2 different WoD sets, same flat values, one set has extra 19% keyflare regen and another doesn't. I'm quite new to the game and I've spent some time trying to understand why there is no difference between those sets when it comes to my GMurphys Waltz of Lemuria tentacle damage generation (Enlighten 1), or why Keyflare Regen Level in Attribute Details doesn't change when you swap those sets.\nTurns out \"Wielder's Keyflare Regen +19%\" doesn't actually mean that the numerical value of your awakener Keyflare Regen Level attribute will increase by 19% once you equip it or enter combat, so I was wrong and stupid and dumb for thinking that Keyflare Regen % will have an effect on GMurphys E1 passive. \nThat being said, there is no way I'm the only one who would think that. I think it's understandable to have that expectation that based on how the WoD description reads, so it would be nice if there was a clear distinction between Keyflare Regen Level as an attribute that is used to scale numerical values on certain awakeners and that deceitful line of text. My sanity greatly affected.", "timestamp": "2025-12-20T00:40:38.173000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-12-20T01:15:45.773000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1451736016737140797", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1085524, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1451736016032628970/1451736016737140797/image.png?ex=69cbc0c6&is=69ca6f46&hm=2c3221d5ae22ce35e50f87e2c05da138a456882c38ab4bd9c12d0819c020ab92&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1451736016032628970", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「Processing」Misleading WoD description/translation, or at least so I think.", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361169005435420785", "1361168939622727801"]}
{"id": "1451851073043173492", "channel_id": "1451736016032628970", "type": 0, "author_id": "198438216628568064", "author_name": "junakaru4ever", "author_bot": false, "content": "Thing is Keyflare Regen and Keyflare Regen Level are two different attributes.\n\nIf it were the same attribute it would have said “Keyflare Regen Level” instead of just “Keyflare Regen” in the WoD description.", "timestamp": "2025-12-20T08:17:49.902000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1451736016032628970", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「Processing」Misleading WoD description/translation, or at least so I think.", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361169005435420785", "1361168939622727801"]}
